nd hazardous marine waste such as fishing wire.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"A Biffa spokesperson said the event had contributed to the worldwide initiative Plastic Free July.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"A Biffa spokesperson said the event had contributed to the worldwide initiative \",\"attributes\":[]}},{\"type\":\"urlLink\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Plastic Free July\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Plastic Free July\",\"attributes\":[]}}],\"locator\":\"https://www.plasticfreejuly.org/\",\"isExternal\":true}},{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\".\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"advertisement\",\"model\":{\"adType\":\"horizontal\"},\"incrementedType\":\"mid_1\"},{\"type\":\"image\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"caption\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Results show dozens of bottles and cans, and even fishing wire have been picket up during the event\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Results show dozens of bottles and cans, and even fishing wire have been picket up during the event\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"altText\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Volunteer in an orange hi viz Biffa jacket collects litter at a beach on an overcast day. He\'s facing away from the camera. Other volunteers can be seen ahead in the distance.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Volunteer in an orange hi viz Biffa jacket collects litter at a beach on an overcast day. He\'s facing away from the camera. Other volunteers can be seen ahead in the distance.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"rawImage\",\"model\":{\"width\":1584,\"height\":891,\"locator\":\"f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg\",\"originCode\":\"cpsprodpb\",\"copyrightH