k/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 976w\" type=\"image/webp\"></source><img alt=\"Amadou Souare\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 976w\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" class=\"ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950\"></picture></span></div><figcaption class=\"ssrcss-179o3th-StyledFigureCaption ehbdhz00\"><span class=\"visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0\">Image caption, </span><div spacing=\"6\" class=\"ssrcss-y7krbn-Stack e1y4nx260\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"Here we live off the land and if it doesn\'t work we are in so much trouble\", says Amadou Souare</p></div></figcaption></figure></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\"><b class=\"ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3\">The UN predicts over 50 million people will be forced to leave their homes by 2020 because their land has turned to desert. This is already happening in Senegal, writes Laeila Adjovi.</b></p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Cattle herder Khalidou Badara took me up a hill in Louga, northern Senegal, to describe to me how his area has changed.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"When I was a child, I did not even dare to walk up to here because the vegetation was so dense. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"But these past few years, the wind and sand have been taking over. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"There are almost no more trees, and the grass does not grow anymore, and so each year, we have to go further and further away to find grazing for our cattle.\"</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">His life has become more complicated because of desertification.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">He\'s not the only one. The UN says land degradation affects 1.5 billion people globally.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Desertification is the persistent degradation of dry land ecosystems by human activities and by climate change. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">It translates into scarcer rains and decreasing soil quality, which leads to less grazing for livestock and lower crop yield.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\"><b class=\"ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3\">Lost land</b></p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Each year, UN figures say, 12 million hectares of land are lost. That\'s land where 20 million tonnes of grain could have been grown.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">People living off the land feel they have no choice but to migrate.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">In another part of Louga - the village of Pendayayake - I met Cheikhou Lo.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"image-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1qlkdz0-ComponentWrapper-FullWidthWrapper ep2nwvo1\"><figure class=\"ssrcss-1vfya96-StyledFigure e34k3c22\"><div class=\"ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21\"><span class=\"ssrcss-5zsoxt-Placeholder etlorgc0\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 976w\" type=\"image/webp\"></source><img alt=\"Cheikhou Lo\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg 976w\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" class=\"ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950\"></picture></span></div><figcaption class=\"ssrcss-179o3th-StyledFigureCaption ehbdhz00\"><span class=\"visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0\">Image caption, </span><div spacing=\"6\" class=\"ssrcss-y7krbn-Stack e1y4nx260\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Cheikhou Lo says he can\'t work because of the drought</p></div></figcaption></figure></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">He had sown hectares of peanuts and beans in the hope of selling them. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">But lack of rain and soil erosion mean the peanuts and beans have not ripened. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">His failed harvest is only good to feed animals. </p></div></div><div data-component=\"image-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1qlkdz0-ComponentWrapper-FullWidthWrapper ep2nwvo1\"><figure class=\"ssrcss-1vfya96-StyledFigure e34k3c22\"><div class=\"ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21\"><span class=\"ssrcss-5zsoxt-Placeholder etlorgc0\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg.webp 976w\" type=\"image/webp\"></source><img alt=\"Peanuts\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/EE7D/production/_86635016_4-cheikhou-lo-holds-unripe-peanuts.jpg 976w\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" class=\"ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950\"></picture></span></div><figcaption class=\"ssrcss-179o3th-StyledFigureCaption ehbdhz00\"><span class=\"visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0\">Image caption, </span><div spacing=\"6\" class=\"ssrcss-y7krbn-Stack e1y4nx260\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Cheikhou Lo\'s peanut harvest has been ruined this year</p></div></figcaption></figure></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"Years ago, there was more rain and we were able to produce more,\" he told me.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"We could live on the crops until the next rainy season. Now, with that drought, we can\'t work. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"If we had boreholes and sufficient means, we could grow vegetables, plant trees, and we could stay here\".</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"But if not, many have to leave and go elsewhere to be able to survive.\"</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\"><b class=\"ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3\">Forced to leave</b></p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">His 27-year-old nephew Amadou Souare added that in the village there is only one borehole and not enough means to dig another one. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"Here we live off the land,\" he said.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"And if that does not work, we are in so much trouble.\" </p></div></div><div data-component=\"image-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1qlkdz0-ComponentWrapper-FullWidthWrapper ep2nwvo1\"><figure class=\"ssrcss-1vfya96-StyledFigure e34k3c22\"><div class=\"ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21\"><span class=\"ssrcss-5zsoxt-Placeholder etlorgc0\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg.webp 976w\" type=\"image/webp\"></source><img alt=\"Peanut farming\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/041D/production/_86635010_3-cheikhou-lo-peanut-field.jpg 976w\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" class=\"ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950\"></picture></span></div><figcaption class=\"ssrcss-179o3th-StyledFigureCaption ehbdhz00\"><span class=\"visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0\">Image caption, </span><div spacing=\"6\" class=\"ssrcss-y7krbn-Stack e1y4nx260\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">There used to be much more rain in northern Senegal</p></div></figcaption></figure></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Many young people from the village have left. Cheikou Lo\'s own children, now adults, went to find jobs in Dakar. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Some have travelled to Gabon, others are planning to go to Europe or Brazil.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"We would rather they stayed here to develop the village but with no jobs and no means, how can we ask them to stay?\" he asked.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"subheadline-block\" class=\"ssrcss-19w8cxh-ComponentWrapper-HeadlineComponentWrapper egtrm1f0\"><h2 id=\"A-wall-of-trees\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"ssrcss-pbttu9-Heading e10rt3ze0\"><span role=\"text\">A wall of trees</span></h2></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">One project is trying to slow the effects of desertification. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">The Great Green Wall initiative aims to create a barrier of vegetation in vulnerable areas across the continent, from Senegal to Djibouti.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">The organisation says hundreds of thousands of trees have already been planted in the region. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">In Senegal, the wall is intended to make a 545km (338 mile) long curtain of vegetation.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"image-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1qlkdz0-ComponentWrapper-FullWidthWrapper ep2nwvo1\"><figure class=\"ssrcss-1vfya96-StyledFigure e34k3c22\"><div class=\"ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21\"><span class=\"ssrcss-5zsoxt-Placeholder etlorgc0\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg.webp 976w\" type=\"image/webp\"></source><img alt=\"Women waiting at a borehole\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/134EB/production/_86638097_10-women-waitingat-borehole.jpg 976w\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" class=\"ssrcss-11yxrdo-Image edrdn950\"></picture></span></div><figcaption class=\"ssrcss-179o3th-StyledFigureCaption ehbdhz00\"><span class=\"visually-hidden ssrcss-1f39n02-VisuallyHidden e16en2lz0\">Image caption, </span><div spacing=\"6\" class=\"ssrcss-y7krbn-Stack e1y4nx260\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">People may not be able to wait the 10 years the trees will take to grow</p></div></figcaption></figure></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">The organisation also makes fodder banks for herders, vegetable gardens to prevent malnutrition and teaches children how to protect the environment.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">The idea is to meet minimal living conditions so people can survive. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">After all, El Hadj Goudiaby from the national agency of the Great Green Wall explained, the trees will only have an impact in 10-15 years\' time.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"Can people here really wait that long? No.\"</p></div></div><div id=\"piano-inline1\"></div><div data-component=\"subheadline-block\" class=\"ssrcss-19w8cxh-ComponentWrapper-HeadlineComponentWrapper egtrm1f0\"><h2 id=\"Pushed-by-the-desert\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"ssrcss-pbttu9-Heading e10rt3ze0\"><span role=\"text\">Pushed by the desert</span></h2></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-uf6wea-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Month by month, people continue to leave. A few hours away, Dakar, the capital city, offers hope of a better life. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Malik Souare grew up in Pendayayake. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Unable to live off the land, he decided to move to Dakar, and found a job as a driver. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">But now, he dreams of going even further away.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">\"You know, everyone wants to get ahead. So I would prefer to leave. Go to England maybe. That is the place where my hopes are now,\" he said.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">For more and more rural communities at the mercy of the environment, migration appears to be the only choice. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">According to the UN, over 50 million people could move from the desertified areas of sub-Saharan Africa towards North Africa and Europe by 2020. </p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\">Pushed by the desert and pulled by opportunity, more and more people like Mr Souare will picture their future abroad.</p></div></div></article></main><aside id=\"mpu-main-aside-content\" data-testid=\"mpu-main-aside-content\" aria-label=\"mpu-main\" aria-hidden=\"true\" label=\"mpu-main\"></aside><aside id=\"content-rec-aside-content\" data-testid=\"content-rec-aside-content\" aria-label=\"content-rec\" aria-hidden=\"true\" label=\"content-rec\"></aside></div><div class=\"ssrcss-115e9m-StyledZone e1mcntqj3\"><aside id=\"topStories-label-aside-content\" data-testid=\"topStories-label-aside-content\" aria-labelledby=\"topStories-label\"><div data-component=\"topStories\" class=\"ssrcss-ykosa2-OnwardJourneysContainerWrapper e1ia0oo99\"><h2 id=\"topStories-label\" type=\"normal\" class=\"ssrcss-ad2rmd-Heading e10rt3ze0\">Top stories</h2><div class=\"ssrcss-17tdcpg-PromoGroupWrapper e1ia0oo98\"><ul role=\"list\" spacing=\"responsive\" class=\"ssrcss-1020bd1-Stack e1y4nx260\"><li class=\"ssrcss-2pgqep-PromoItem e1ia0oo97\"><div data-testid=\"promo\" class=\"ssrcss-8745b4-Promo e1vyq2e80\"><div class=\"ssrcss-1djxueb-PromoCompact e18gnqux0\"><div class=\"ssrcss-1d68cot-PromoContent exn3ah913\"><div s