\\"Here we live off the land and if it doesn\'t work we are in so much trouble\\\\\\\", says Amadou Souare\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}}]}},\\\"image\\\":{\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Amadou Souare\\\",\\\"copyright\\\":null,\\\"height\\\":549,\\\"width\\\":976,\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg\\\",\\\"srcSet\\\":\\\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg.webp 976w\\\",\\\"mimeType\\\":\\\"image/webp\\\",\\\"fallbackSrcSets\\\":[{\\\"mimeType\\\":\\\"image/jpeg\\\",\\\"srcSet\\\":\\\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/800/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/A05D/production/_86635014_6-amadou-souare-field.jpg 976w\\\"}],\\\"loading\\\":\\\"eager\\\"}}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"The UN predicts over 50 million people will be forced to leave their homes by 2020 because their land has turned to desert. This is already happening in Senegal, writes Laeila Adjovi.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"The UN predicts over 50 million people will be forced to leave their homes by 2020 because their land has turned to desert. This is already happening in Senegal, writes Laeila Adjovi.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[\\\"bold\\\"]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cattle herder Khalidou Badara took me up a hill in Louga, northern Senegal, to describe to me how his area has changed.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cattle herder Khalidou Badara took me up a hill in Louga, northern Senegal, to describe to me how his area has changed.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"When I was a child, I did not even dare to walk up to here because the vegetation was so dense. \\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"When I was a child, I did not even dare to walk up to here because the vegetation was so dense. \\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"But these past few years, the wind and sand have been taking over. \\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"But these past few years, the wind and sand have been taking over. \\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"There are almost no more trees, and the grass does not grow anymore, and so each year, we have to go further and further away to find grazing for our cattle.\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"There are almost no more trees, and the grass does not grow anymore, and so each year, we have to go further and further away to find grazing for our cattle.\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"His life has become more complicated because of desertification.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"His life has become more complicated because of desertification.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"He\'s not the only one. The UN says land degradation affects 1.5 billion people globally.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"He\'s not the only one. The UN says land degradation affects 1.5 billion people globally.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Desertification is the persistent degradation of dry land ecosystems by human activities and by climate change. \\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Desertification is the persistent degradation of dry land ecosystems by human activities and by climate change. \\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"It translates into scarcer rains and decreasing soil quality, which leads to less grazing for livestock and lower crop yield.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"It translates into scarcer rains and decreasing soil quality, which leads to less grazing for livestock and lower crop yield.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Lost land\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Lost land\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[\\\"bold\\\"]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Each year, UN figures say, 12 million hectares of land are lost. That\'s land where 20 million tonnes of grain could have been grown.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Each year, UN figures say, 12 million hectares of land are lost. That\'s land where 20 million tonnes of grain could have been grown.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"People living off the land feel they have no choice but to migrate.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"People living off the land feel they have no choice but to migrate.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"In another part of Louga - the village of Pendayayake - I met Cheikhou Lo.\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"In another part of Louga - the village of Pendayayake - I met Cheikhou Lo.\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}}]}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"caption\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"paragraph\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cheikhou Lo says he can\'t work because of the drought\\\",\\\"blocks\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"fragment\\\",\\\"model\\\":{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cheikhou Lo says he can\'t work because of the drought\\\",\\\"attributes\\\":[]}}]}}]}},\\\"image\\\":{\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Cheikhou Lo\\\",\\\"copyright\\\":null,\\\"height\\\":549,\\\"width\\\":976,\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/976/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg\\\",\\\"srcSet\\\":\\\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/320/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/15813/production/_86638088_2-cheikou-lo.jpg.webp 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/624/cpsprod