&ldquo;It makes sense to hold this Cop in an arid country.&rdquo; He said the kingdom&rsquo;s government had already embarked on a series of initiatives to restore land, protect water sources and conserve biodiversity.</p><p class=\"dcr-16w5gq9\">For instance, the country is working to preserve a system of terraces on a mountain range parallel to the Red Sea, where rainfall is harvested. The Saudi Green Initiative has a target of restoring 40m hectares of degraded land by 2030.</p><p class=\"dcr-16w5gq9\">Just as many countries agreed at the biodiversity Cop16 in Cali, Colombia, to conserve at least 30% of their land, Faqeeha hopes that countries will make commitments to restore their areas of highly degraded land at the CCD Cop. &ldquo;Not all countries have targets yet on restoring lands,&rdquo; he noted. &ldquo;And we also need to prevent degradation, by better land management.&rdquo;</p></div></div><gu-island name=\"SlotBodyEnd\" priority=\"feature\" deferuntil=\"visible\" props=\'{\"contentType\":\"Article\",\"contributionsServiceUrl\":\"https://contributions.guardianapis.com\",\"idApiUrl\":\"https://idapi.theguardian.com\",\"isMinuteArticle\":false,\"isPaidContent\":false,\"pageId\":\"environment/2024/nov/04/degradation-of-land-is-threat-to-human-life-saudi-government-says\",\"sectionId\":\"environment\",\"shouldHideReaderRevenue\":false,\"tags\":[{\"id\":\"environment/soil\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Soil\"},{\"id\":\"environment/conservation\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Conservation\"},{\"id\":\"world/world\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"World news\"},{\"id\":\"world/saudiarabia\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Saudi Arabia\"},{\"id\":\"environment/desertification\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Desertification\"},{\"id\":\"environment/drought\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Drought\"},{\"id\":\"environment/environment\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Environment\"},{\"id\":\"environment/water\",\"type\":\"Keyword\",\"title\":\"Wat