nother lost decade for nature slip past,\\\" said Beccy Speight, chief executive of the RSPB.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Biodiversity is declining faster than at any time in human history. Since 1970, there has been on average almost a 70% decline in the populations of mammals, birds, fish, reptiles and amphibians.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Biodiversity is declining faster than at any time in human history. Since 1970, there has been on average almost a 70% decline in the populations of mammals, birds, fish, reptiles and amphibians.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"advertisement\",\"model\":{\"adType\":\"horizontal\"},\"incrementedType\":\"mid_5\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"It is thought that one million animal and plant species - almost a quarter of the global total - are threatened with extinction.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"It is thought that one million animal and plant species - almost a quarter of the global total - are threatened with extinction.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Follow Helen on Twitter.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Follow Helen \",\"attributes\":[]}},{\"type\":\"urlLink\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"on Twitter.\",\"locator\":\"https://twitter.com/hbriggs\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"on Twitter.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"links\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"link\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Talks resume on global plan to protect nature\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"urlLink\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Talks resume on global plan to protect nature\",\"locator\":\"/news/science-environment-583062