             <section class=\"article-content__editor \">\n                <!-- content from cms -->\n                <!--0--><p></p><div class=\"video-container\"><iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen src=\"https://video.udn.com/embed/news/1305227\"></iframe></div><p>\r\n今天凌晨<a href=\"/search/tagging/2/%E7%99%BD%E6%B2%99%E5%B1%AF%E5%AA%BD%E7%A5%96\" rel=\"白沙屯媽祖\" data-rel=\"/2/105182\" class=\"tag\"><strong>白沙屯媽祖</strong></a>在拱天宮起駕登轎儀式時，雲林縣長張麗善為與台中市長盧秀燕不被擋住，伸出雙手將前方爐主移開，雖很有禮貌「移位」，但被報導後引來網友痛斥，張麗善今天公開致歉，表示她不識爐主身份，無意中有不周之處，絕非出於本意。</p><!--1--><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n「粉紅超跑」苗栗白沙屯拱天宮媽祖進香，今天凌晨起駕出發前往北港朝天宮，雲林縣長張麗善昨晚也趕往拱天宮接駕，恭迎白沙屯媽祖上轎，在媽祖登轎儀式時，她突然伸出雙手將原本站在在前方的爐主「請移」旁邊，整個過程都被眾多鏡頭拍下來，引來眾多網友一陣撻伐。</p><style>\r\n/*.innity-apps-underlay-ad {z-index: 34 !important; }*/\r\n.innity-apps-underlay-ad ~ .header {z-index: 35;}\r\n.innity-apps-underlay-ad ~ .main-content .inline-ads { background: transparent;}\r\n#eyeDiv ~ .footer{ position: relative; z-index: 2;} /* sizmek_underlay 投遞調整置底 z-index 權重 */\r\n.article-content__abbr__text {display:inline-block;} /* to be remove */\r\n</style>\r\n<!-- /129853887/udn.com/2_News/3_News-Mobile/4_News-Mobile-a02 ※Mobile文中大佈告_3000x250※內容頁-->\r\n<div class=\"inline-ads\">\r\n<div class=\"udn-ads udn-ads--mobile\" id=\"ads-inline\" style=\"min-height: 250px;\">\r\n  <script>\r\n    googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'ads-inline\'); });\r\n  </script>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"underlay-checkpoint\"></div>\r\n<!-- innity_underlay直售 -->\r\n<span id=\"innity-custom-premium-span-9661\"></span>\r\n<!-- innity_underlay聯播 -->\r\n<span id=\"innity-custom-adnetwork-span-67883\"></span>\r\n\r\n</div><div class=\"inline-ads inline-ads--desktop\">\r\n  <!-- /4576170/free-1_News-PC-a23   新聞網 PC 文中廣告 (左)影音 -->\r\n  <div class=\"udn-ads\" id=\"ads-inline-Desktop\" style=\"width: 442.7px; min-height: 250px;\">\r\n    <script>\r\n      googletag.cmd.push(function() { \r\n        var sizeMapping = googletag.sizeMapping(). \r\n 